cvc5: cvc5 (a first-order theorem prover and SMT solver)
cvc5:
cvc5: CVC5 is an automated theorem prover and satisfiability modulo
cvc5: theories (SMT) solver. Given a formula in first-order logic, it
cvc5: attempts to either prove the formula or find a counterexample. CVC5
cvc5: supports arithmetic, reasoning about arrays, and several other
cvc5: built-in theories. Input problems are written in SMT-LIB format.
cvc5:
cvc5: This package includes the cvc5 program as well as libraries.
cvc5:
cvc5: Homepage: https://cvc5.cs.stanford.edu/
